platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Theres nothing like a cute llama to help you stay on top of your hydration goals. All you have to do? Track the liquid you consume with Waterllama. Doing so unlocks a world of characters and tools that help you monitor your overall hydration and create goals that are right for you. Timely reminders and a variety of challenges are also there to help you manage an important part of your well-being with joy.
